
Contenido recomendado para proyectos .NET:

```gitignore
# Build folders
bin/
obj/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# User-specific files
*.user
*.suo

# Logs
*.log

# EF Core Migrations metadata
ConsoleApp/Migrations/*Designer.cs

# Database files (important for privacy)
*.mdf
*.ldf
*.bak

# VS Code workspace junk
*.slnx